Text: This is really strange, everything sounds just fine and nothing seems wrong, but Banshee is displaying some very strange track stats.  For instance, one song is 16kpbs bitrate, but sounds fine, and another is at 400-something kpbs.  One song thinks it's 24 minutes long, though it only plays for the normal 3:56.  Again, everything sounds fine, and thanks for the upload, but I wonder what happened.  Could just be my software, though it's never done anything like this before.
